quran[89]{c,v,t}:
  43,1,Ha mim
  43,2,Ndilumbira pali Buku limene limafotokoza zinthu mosabisa
  43,3,Ndithudi talipanga ilo kukhala Korani yam’chinenero cha Chiarabu kuti iwe ukhoza kulizindikira
  43,4,"Ndithudi ilo lili mu Make Buku limene lili pamaso pathu, lolemekezeka ndi lodzala ndi nzeru"
  43,5,Kodi Ife tisiye kukukumbutsani inu nonse chifukwa chakuti ndinu anthu osasamala ndi oswa malamulo
  43,6,Kodi ndi Atumwi angati amene Ife tidatumiza ku mitundu ya anthu akale
  43,7,Ndipo kwa iwo sikunadze Mtumwi amene iwo sadamunyoze
  43,8,"Kotero Ife tidawaononga, anthu amphamvu kuposa awa, ndipo chitsanzo cha anthu onse akale chadutsa"
  43,9,"Ndithudi ngati iwe ukawafunsa kuti, “Kodi ndani adalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi?” Iwo, ndithudi, adzakuyankha kuti, “Mwini mphamvu ndi Mwini wodziwa ndiye amene adazilenga.”"
  43,10,Iye ndi amene adalenga dziko kukhala malo anu a mpumulo ndipo adaika mu ilo njira kuti inu mukhoza kutsogozedwa bwino
  43,11,"Ndipo ndiye amene amatumiza mvula kuchokera kumitambo molingana ndi muyeso. Ndipo Ife timadzutsa nthaka imene idali yakufa ndi iyo, kotero nanunso mudzadzutsidwa chimodzimodzi"
  43,12,Ndipo ndiye amene adalenga zinthu ziwiriziwiri ndipo adapanga zombo ndi nyama kuti muzikwera
  43,13,"Kuti inu mukhoza kukhala okhazikika pa misana pawo ndi kukumbukira ubwino wa Ambuye wanu pamene mumakhazikikapo ndi kunena kuti, “Ulemerero ukhale kwa Iye amene adazipanga izo kukhala zopanda mphamvu kwa ife ndipo ife sitikadatha kutero.”"
  43,14,“Ndithudi kwa Ambuye wathu ife tidzabwerera.”
  43,15,Komabe iwo amawapatsa ena mwa akapolo ake gawo lake. Ndithudi munthu ndi wosayamika
  43,16,Kodi Iye wadzisankhira ana aakazi kuchokera ku zimene walenga ndipo adakusankhani inu kukhala ndi ana aamuna
  43,17,"Ndipo ngati wina wa iwo auzidwa nkhani za chimene Iye amati ndi chofanana ndi Mulungu, nkhope yake imada ndipo amakhala wokwiya"
  43,18,"Icho ndi chimene chidapangidwa ngati chosangalatsa ndipo pa mtsutso, icho sichingathe kuyankhula bwinobwino"
  43,19,"Ndipo iwo amasandutsa angelo amene ali akapolo a Mulungu, kukhala akazi. Kodi iwo adaonerera chilengedwe chawo? Umboni wawo udzalembedwa ndipo iwo adzafunsidwa"
  43,20,"Ndipo iwo adati, “Chikadakhala chifuniro cha Mwini Chisoni Chosatha, ife sitikadapembedza milungu ina.” Iwo sadziwa china chilichonse chokhudza chimenechi. Ndipo iwo amangonama chabe"
  43,21,Kodi kapena Ife tidawapatsa Buku lina ili lisanadze limene iwo ali kukhulupilira
  43,22,"Iyayi! Iwo amati, “Ife tidapeza makolo athu ali kutsatira njira ina ndi chipembedzo china chake ndipo ife timatsogozedwa potsatira zimene iwo amachita.”"
  43,23,"Ndipo Ife sitidatumize Mchenjezi iwe usanadze kwa anthu ena, koma achuma amene anali kukhala pakati pawo ankati; “Ife tidapeza makolo athu ali kutsatira njira yina ndi chipembedzo china chake ndipo ndithudi ife tidzatsatira zimene iwo anali kuchita.”"
  43,24,"Iye adati; “Ngakhale kuti ine nditakubweretserani langizo labwino loposa limene mukuti mudapeza makolo anu ali kutsatira?” Iwo adati, “Ndithudi ife sitikhulupirira zimene iwe ukuti watumizidwa.”"
  43,25,Kotero Ife tidagwetsa chilango pa iwo ndipo taona mmene chinalili chimaliziro cha iwo amene adakana choonadi
  43,26,"Ndipo Abrahamu adawauza abambo ake pamodzi ndi anthu ake kuti, “Ndithudi ine ndili kudzipatula ku zimene inu mupembedza.”"
  43,27,"“Kupatula yekhayo amene adandilenga ine ndipo, ndithudi, Iye adzanditsogolera.”"
  43,28,Ndipo adawapanga mawu kuti akhazikike mwa iwo amene adadza iye atachoka kuti akhoza kubwerera
  43,29,"Iyayi! Koma Ine ndidawapatsa ,iwo ndiponso makolo awo, chisangalalo mpaka pamene choonadi chidadza kwa iwo ndi Mtumwi amene anali kuwafotokozera zonse momveka"
  43,30,"Koma pamene choonadi chidadza pa iwo, iwo adati, “Awa ndi matsenga ndipo ife sitikhulupirira mwa iwo.”"
  43,31,"Ndipo iwo amati: “Bwanji Korani iyi siidatumizidwe kwa munthu wina wotchuka wochokera ku Mzinda wina pakati pa Mizinda iwiri?”"
  43,32,Kodi ndiwo amene akhoza kugawa gawo lina la chisomo cha Ambuye wako? Ndife amene timagawa pakati pawo chakudya chawo cha moyo uno ndipo tawakweza ena kukhala apamwamba kuposa anzawo kotero kuti akhoza kulemba ntchito anzawo. Koma chisoni cha Ambuye wako ndi chabwino kwambiri kuposa chuma chimene amasonkhanitsa
  43,33,"Ndipo zikadakhala kuti anthu onse anali a chipembedzo chimodzi, ndithudi, Ife tikadawapatsa onse amene sakhulupirira mwa Mulungu madenga a siliva kuti aike pa nyumba zawo ndi pa makwerero oti azikwererapo"
  43,34,"Ndipo nyumba, zitseko ndi mipando, zonse zikadakhala za siliva kuti azikhalapo"
  43,35,"Ndipo zipangizo zina zikadakhala za golide. Komabe zonsezi sizikadakhala chinthu china koma chisangalalo cha m’moyo uno. Ndipo moyo umene uli nkudza, umene uli ndi Ambuye wako, ndi wa anthu ochita ntchito zabwino"
  43,36,"Aliyense amene asiya kukumbukira Mwini chisoni chosatha, Ife timamusankhira iye Satana kuti akhale bwenzi lake la pamtima"
  43,37,"Ndipo, ndithudi, iwo amangowasokoneza ku njira yoyenera koma iwo amaganiza kuti ali kutsogozedwa bwino"
  43,38,"Mpaka pamene wotereyu abwerera kwa Ife, iye amati, pomuuza bwenzi lake la pamtima, “Kukadakhala kuti pakati pa ine ndi iwe panali mtunda wotalika monga kutalikirana kwa kum’mawa kuwiri!” Bwenzi loipa lenileni"
  43,39,"Ndipo popeza inu munali kuchita zoipa, lero sizidzakuthandizani popeza nonse ndinu olandira chilango"
  43,40,Kodi iwe ungawapange agonthi kumva kapena kutsogolera anthu akhungu kapena kutsogolera iye amene ndi ochimwa
  43,41,"Ndipo Ife tikakutenga, Ife, ndithudi, tidzagwetsa chilango chathu pa iwo"
  43,42,"Kapena ngati Ife titakuonetsa zina zimene tawalonjeza iwo, ndipo ndithudi, Ife tili ndi mphamvu pa zinthu zonse"
  43,43,Kotero gwiritsa chimene chavumbulutsidwa kwa iwe. Ndithudi iwe uli pa njira yoyenera
  43,44,Ndipo ndithudi Ichi ndi chikumbutso kwa iwe ndi kwa anthu ako ndipo posachedwapa mudzafunsidwa
  43,45,Ndipo afunse iwo za Atumwi athu amene Ife tidawatuma iwe usanabadwe. Kodi Ife tidasankha milungu ina yoti izipembedzedwa yoonjezera pa Mwini Chisoni Chosatha
  43,46,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ife tidamutumiza Mose ndi uthenga wathu kwa Farawo ndi mafumu ake ndipo iye adati, “Ndithudi ine ndine Mtumwi wa Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse.”"
  43,47,"Koma pamene iye adadza kwa iwo ndi zizindikiro zathu zooneka, iwo adaziseka zizindikirozo"
  43,48,"Tidawaonetsa zizindikiro zosiyanasiyana, chilichonse chopambana chinzake, ndipo Ife tidawapatsa chilango kuti akhoza kutembenuka"
  43,49,"Ndipo iwo adati, “oh iwe munthu wamatsenga! Mupemphe Ambuye wako m’malo mwathu, molingana ndi lonjezo limene Iye adapanga ndi iwe. Ndithudi ife tidzatsatira njira yoyenera.”"
  43,50,"Koma pamene tidawachotsera chilango, iwo adaphwanya lonjezo lawo"
  43,51,"Ndipo Farawo adalengeza pamaso pa anthu ake kuti, “Oh inu anthu anga! Kodi Ufumu wa dziko la Aiguputo si wanga? Nanga mitsinje imene ilikuyenda pansi pa mapazi anga, kodi simuli kuiona?”"
  43,52,“Kodi ine sindine wopambana kwambiri kuposa munthu wonyozeka amene ali kukanika kuyankhula momveka?”
  43,53,“Nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani iye sadavekedwe zigwinjiri za golide kapena bwanji silinadze ndi iye gulu la angelo lomuperekeza?”
  43,54,Motero iye adawapusitsa anthu ake ndipo iwo amamumvera iye. Ndithudi iwo adali anthu onyoza
  43,55,"Ndipo pamene iwo adatikwiyitsa, Ife tidawagwetsera chilango ndipo onse tidawamiza m’madzi"
  43,56,Ndipo tidawapanga iwo kukhala phunziro kwa mibadwo yam’tsogolo
  43,57,"Ndipo pamene mwana wamwamuna wa Maria atchulidwa ngati chitsanzo, taona! Anthu ako amaseka"
  43,58,"Ndipo iwo amati, “Kodi milungu yathu ndiyo yopambana kapena iyeyo ndiye wopambana?” Izi amangozinena kwa iwe ndi cholinga chofuna mikangano ndipo iwo ndi anthu amwano"
  43,59,"Iye sadali wina koma kapolo wathu amene tidamulangiza chisomo chathu, ndipo tidamupanga Iye kukhala chitsanzo kwa ana a Israyeli"
  43,60,Ndipo tikadafuna tikadapanga ena a inu kukhala angelo kuti akhale padziko m’malo mwanu
  43,61,"Ndithudi ichi ndi chizindikiro cha ola, kotero musakayike za ilo ndipo nditsateni ine. Iyo ndiyo njira yoyenera"
  43,62,"Ndipo musalole kuti Satana akutchinjirizeni chifukwa, ndithudi, iye ndi mdani wanu weniweni"
  43,63,"Pamene Yesu adadza ndi zizindikiro zooneka adati, “Tsopano ndadza kwa inu ndi luntha ndi cholinga chokuuzani tsatanetsatane za fundo zina zimene mumatsutsana. Motero opani Mulungu ndipo mundimvere ine.”"
  43,64,“Ndithudi Mulungu! Ndiye Ambuye wanga ndi Ambuye wanu. Motero mutumikireni Iye. Imeneyi ndiyo njira yoyenera.”
  43,65,"Koma magulu ena a pakati pawo adapatukana, kotero tsoka kwa iwo amene adali oipa chifukwa cha chilango chowawa chimene chidzadza pa iwo patsiku la masautso"
  43,66,Kodi iwo ali kungodikira kuti ola lidzadza pa iwo mwadzidzidzi pamene iwo sali kudziwa
  43,67,Abwenzi patsiku limeneli adzasanduka adani kupatula okhawo amene amalewa zoipa
  43,68,oh inu akapolo anga! Palibe chochititsa mantha kwa inu lero lino ndipo simudzamva chisoni
  43,69,Inu amene mwakhulupirira chivumbulutso chathu ndipo munali Asilamu
  43,70,"Lowani m’Paradiso, inu pamodzi ndi akazi anu ndipo mudzasangalatsidwa"
  43,71,Mbale za golide ndi zikho zomwera zidzaperekedwa kwa iwo ndipo mu izo mudzakhala zimene mitima yawo inali kulakalaka ndi ponso zosangalala kuziona. Ndipo inu mudzakhala momwemo mpaka kalekale
  43,72,Ndipo uwu ndi munda umene mwapatsidwa kuti mukhalemo chifukwa cha zimene mudachita
  43,73,M’menemo mudzapeza zipatso zochuluka zimene muzidzadya
  43,74,Ndithudi onse osakhulupirira adzakhala ku moto wa ku Gahena mpaka kalekale
  43,75,Chilango chawo sichidzachepetsedwa ndipo adzasowa chonena chifukwa adzakhala ndi mantha
  43,76,Ife sitidawalakwire koma iwo adadzilakwitsa okha
  43,77,"Ndipo iwo adzalira kuti, “Oh Maliki! Muuze Ambuye wako kuti atimalize ife! Ndipo iye adzati, “Ndithudi inu mudzakhalabe ndi moyo.”"
  43,78,Ndithudi Ife tabweretsa choonadi kwa iwe koma ambiri a inu mumadana ndi choonadi
  43,79,Kapene iwo ali ndi chikonzekero china? Motero nafenso tili kukonzeka
  43,80,Kapena iwo amaganiza kuti Ife sitikumva zimene amabisa ndi nkhani zawo za chinsinsi? Ndithudi Ife timamva ndipo Atumwi athu amene ali pakati pawo amalemba chilichonse
  43,81,"Nena, “Ngati Mwini Chisoni Chosatha akadakhala ndi Mwana, ine ndikadakhala woyamba kumupembedza.”"
  43,82,"“Ulemerero ukhale kwa Ambuye wakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi, Ambuye Mwini mpando wachifumu! Iye akhale pamwamba pa zimene amukundukira Iye.”"
  43,83,Kotero aleke kuti ayambe kuyankhula zinthu zopanda pake ndi kusewera mpaka pamene akumana ndi tsiku limene amaopsedwa nalo
  43,84,Iye ndiye Mulungu wakumwamba ndi Mulungu wa padziko lapansi ndipo Iye ndi waluntha ndi wodziwa chinthu china chilichonse
  43,85,Ndipo wodala ndi Mwini Ufumu wakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ndi zonse zimene zili m’menemo. Iye ndiye amene amadziwa ola lachiweruzo ndipo kwa Iye ndi kumene nonse mudzabwerera
  43,86,Ndipo onse amene amawapembedza oonjezera pa Mulungu alibe mphamvu yowaimirira kupatula yekhayo amene amachitira umboni woona ndiye amene iwo amamudziwa
  43,87,"Ndipo ngati iwe utawafunsa kuti kodi adawalenga ndani? Ndithudi iwo adzayankha kuti, “Mulungu.” Nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani amasiya choonadi"
  43,88,"Ndi zonena zake kuti, “Ambuye wanga! Ndithudi awa ndi anthu amene safuna kukhulupirira.”"
  43,89,"Kotero asiye okha ndipo nena, “Mtendere!” Koma iwo adzadziwa posachedwapa"